<subSubSection id="D01AE5968463D34E70EAA853C9093558" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" type="notes">
<paragraph id="0459105DEE69BDE835960C6BFD5BB00E" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E570769D5CFE223562F69A23EA73096B" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">
This species is included in 
<taxonomicName id="B672499530F9AAA1FD8037A46A7979C3" authority="P.M.Peterson, K.Romaschenko, R.J.Soreng &amp; S.P.Sylvester, 2020" authorityName="P. M. Peterson, Romasch., Soreng &amp; Sylvester" authorityYear="2020" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Alpagrostis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Alpagrostis" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C25A71920AF6ABAE0AB41F474B64ECEB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Alpagrostis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on its similar morphology, although this needs to be confirmed in molecular analyses. Certain characteristics sometimes differ from the other species in the genus, i.e., spikelets and lemmas sometimes shorter, insertion of the awn sometimes higher on the lemma, panicle branches and pedicels smooth or scaberulous. 
<taxonomicName id="D962D1AF3560A79A6FDBD06E5FA493D9" authority="P.M.Peterson, K.Romaschenko, R.J.Soreng &amp; S.P.Sylvester, 2020" authorityName="P. M. Peterson, Romasch., Soreng &amp; Sylvester" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="P. M. Peterson, Romasch., Soreng &amp; Sylvester" baseAuthorityYear="2020" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Alpagrostis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Alpagrostis barceloi" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="barceloi">
<emphasis id="6222BBA941DE7B2ABE3E45AD4167012D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Alpagrostis barceloi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shares with other member of the genus, conduplicate leaf blades, truncate lemma apices with setaceous extensions of the lateral veins, and ecologically is a strict orophyte, much like 
<taxonomicName id="B2E0AB80A3565E71DC2721485BEBFC36" genus="A." lsidName="A. alpina" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="C437EC73740AD63CB8466895F7446BAB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">A. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="D40217C6DE268F77F82A606B24066728" genus="A." lsidName="A. schleicheri" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" rank="species" species="schleicheri">
<emphasis id="44AB1E657AA4C3E087C7A731F81FE50A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">A. schleicheri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="980BF53DB23303A83AE2B254193974C1" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.2000.tb01551.x" author="Saez, L" journalOrPublisher="Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" pagination="359 - 370" refId="B35" refString="Saez, L, Rossello, JA, 2000. A new species of Agrostis (Gramineae) in the A. alpina complex. Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society 133 (3): 359 - 370, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.2000.tb01551.x" title="A new species of Agrostis (Gramineae) in the A. alpina complex." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.2000.tb01551.x" volume="133" year="2000">
<normalizedToken id="719C1C7990F2281B4F9292635E29B888" originalValue="Sáez">Saez</normalizedToken>
and 
<normalizedToken id="822B02B7AA9E5A14330D03F47AA4C7A0" originalValue="Rosselló">Rossello</normalizedToken>
2000
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
